{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_10_03",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜 3話 はい、大好きです",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――怜が洞窟に入ってから数時間後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Several hours after Rei entered the cave",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1633.3333333,
          "startTime": 1.6333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……\nようやく地上に戻れた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hah‚ hah…\nI finally made it back to the surface…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "よく帰って来たな。お疲れ様",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good job coming back. You did well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.4333339572,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.3666672905
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……\nちゃんと私が戻るのを待っててくれたんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…\nYou really waited for me to return.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……{user}さんの顔を見ると\n緊張が解けてホッとします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe… when I see your face‚\nmy tension melts away and I feel relieved.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.4333339572
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "緊張感のない顔で悪かったな\nそれで、絶景は見れたのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry for having such a relaxed face.\nSo‚ were you able to see the scenic view?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.5000006239
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "それが、聞いて下さい！\n洞窟の中に湖があったんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ please listen!\nThere was a lake inside the cave!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "洞窟の天井に穴が空いてて光が差し込んでいたんですが\n光の加減によって水面が青く煌めいて見えるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There was a hole in the cave ceiling with light streaming in‚\nand depending on the light‚ the water surface appeared to shimmer blue.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.3000006239
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "とても幻想的な光景で\nカメラの前なのに喋るのも忘れて見とれてしまいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was such a fantastic sight\nthat even though I was in front of the camera‚ I forgot to speak and was mesmerized.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "凄く神秘的で、息を呑むくらい綺麗な景色で……\nみんなにも見せたかったな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was so mystical and breathtakingly beautiful…\nI wish I could have shown it to everyone too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.9000006239
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "綺麗な景色を見た最初の感想が\n「みんなにも見せたかった」か……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your first impression of seeing beautiful scenery\nwas \"I wish I could have shown it to everyone too\"…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "サニピのみんなと嬉しさや楽しさを分かち合うのは\n怜にとって当たり前のことになっているんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sharing happiness and joy with everyone in Sunny Peace\nhas become natural for you‚ Rei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.1666672905
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね……今の私には、みんなと一緒に過ごして\nみんなと喜びを共有するのが当たり前のことなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right… for me now‚ spending time with everyone\nand sharing joy with them is natural.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "無人島のロケでは、みんなに振り回されましたけど\n同じくらいみんなに助けられました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "On the deserted island shoot‚ everyone gave me trouble‚ but\nthey helped me just as much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.4999974568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.5666647474
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "私一人だったら無人島の生活に耐えられなかった……\nみんなと一緒だったから最後までやり遂げられたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I had been alone‚ I couldn't have endured life on the deserted island…\nBecause I was with everyone‚ I could see it through to the end.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.0999974568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "怜はサニピのみんなのことが大好きなんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You really love everyone in Sunny Peace‚ don't you‚ Rei?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.133331414,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.3666647474
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "はい、大好きです\n……って、何を言わせるんですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I love them.\n…Wait‚ what are you making me say?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.6999974568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.733331414
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ……こんな恥ずかしいことを言うなんて\n歩き疲れて頭が回らなくなってるのかも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… saying such embarrassing things -\nmaybe I'm so tired from walking that my head isn't working…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.5333307902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "照れくさいので、今話したことは……\nみんなには内緒にして下さいね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since it's embarrassing‚ please…\nkeep it a secret from everyone‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.3333307902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "分かったよ。ここだけの秘密だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand. It's just between us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.1666647474,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.1666647474
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.1999980807
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（でも、怜がサニピのみんなを好きな気持ちは）\n（みんなにはとっくにバレてると思うぞ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（But I think everyone already knows how much）\n（Rei loves everyone in Sunny Peace）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.1333307902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数週間後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Several weeks later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.7999980807,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 147.0333307902
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "怜が出演した番組、オンエアされたのを観たよ\n地底湖が神秘的で本当に綺麗だったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I watched the broadcast of the show you appeared on‚ Rei.\nThe underground lake was mystical and truly beautiful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.9906541796,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "私も寮でみんなと一緒に観ました\nそうしたら、さくら達に羨ましがられて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I watched it at the dorm with everyone too.\nThen Sakura and the others were envious…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.9333307902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "私も行きたかっただの、一人で見て来たなんて\nずるいだの、不満を言われてしまいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They complained‚ saying things like‚ \"I wanted to go too‚\"\nand \"It’s not fair you went and saw it alone.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.9834543228,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03-rei016.m4a",
      "text": "という訳で、今度お仕事で絶景を見に行く時は\nみんなで行かせて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So next time there's a job to go see some see scenic views‚\nplease let us all go together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.3666641235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_10_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "みんながいれば怜が一人で寂しい思いを\nすることもないし、その方がいいかもしれないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If everyone's there‚ Rei won't have to\nfeel lonely alone‚ so that might be better.",
        "id": ""
      },
